  "text": "the ergodic secrecy rate of the AN transmission scheme and investigated the optimal power allocation for the maximization of the secrecy rate. Considering slow fading channels where the channel coherence time is larger than the codeword period, [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] examined the secrecy outage probability of the AN transmission scheme. More recently, [CITATION_3] , [CITATION_4] investigated not only the secrecy outage probability but the throughput of the AN transmission scheme. Given a secrecy outage constraint, [CITATION_5] optimized the wiretap code rate to maximize the average throughput of non-adaptive encoding (NAE) and adaptive encoding (AE) schemes under the assumption of zero noise at the eavesdropper. Different from [CITATION_6] , we considered non-zero noise at the eavesdropper in [CITATION_7] and determined the optimal secrecy rate that maximizes the secrecy throughput.",
